      <title class="- topic/title ">
         <ph class="- topic/ph " props="autonumber">1.403</ph> Individual deviations.</title>
      <conbody class="- topic/body concept/conbody ">
         <p id="d41e8" class="- topic/p ">Individual deviations affect only one contract action, and, unless <xref href="1.405.dita#FAR_1_405"
                  base="i1126671"
                  outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                  class="- topic/xref ">1.405</xref>(e) is applicable, may be authorized by the agency head. The contracting officer must document the justification and agency approval in the contract file.</p>
      </conbody>
